data.description: Elegantly Expansive Residence in the coveted Gentilly Terrace/Dillard enclave, this home seamlessly marries multi-functionality with location. Once a duplex and now transformed into a single-family, it's just a brief 1.5-mile to City Park. Anchored on a generous 40’x127’ plot, dual driveways lead to an inviting backyard. The layout features a total of 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, offering great potential to convert back to a duplex and create separate living spaces with 2 bedrooms and 1 bath on each level, along with spacious living areas for each floor. There is tremendous potential for either a duplex conversion or accommodating an extended family, making it an excellent multifamily investment opportunity. With individual electric metering already in place for each unit, the option for a duplex transformation remains effortlessly within reach, offering a tantalizing future investment prospect. Flood zone X. Property qualifies for 100% Finance NO PMI with Hancock Whitney Bank.
